Remove variable labels.

Source: R/ff_label.R
remove_labels.Rd

Remove variable labels.

remove_labels(.data)

Arguments

.data

Data frame

Value

The original data frame with variable label attributes removed.

Examples

colon_s %>%
  remove_labels()
